# fpm-py

A Python library for Fourier Ptychographic Microscopy (FPM) simulation and reconstruction.

- **Forward & Backward Models**: Simulate FPM captures and reconstruct high-resolution images

## Installation

```bash
uv add fpm-py
# or : pip install fpm-py
```

## Usage

See main.py
